    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Like-new, exceptionally well-kept vehicle in outstanding condition throughout. The exterior presents beautifully with a clean, glossy finish and minimal to no noticeable cosmetic wear, while the interior is equally impressive with a fresh, well-cared-for appearance. It has clearly been maintained to a very high standard and should appeal to buyers looking for a top-tier, turn-key car that needs nothing but a new owner.",
