    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with real value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a practical budget option and is best suited for someone looking for a low-cost way into ownership or a solid project opportunity. Represented honestly and priced accordingly, it delivers a chance to secure dependable utility at an accessible price point.",
