      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it starts, runs, and could make a great cheap runabout, first car, or tidy-up project for someone handy. If you\u2019re after something affordable and straightforward with no surprises about it being a used car, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with good bones and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. The drivetrain fires up and runs, the chassis feels like a strong foundation, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for a budget daily, weekend wrenching project, or parts saver. It shows its age cosmetically and will need attention in spots, but for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance, this is an honest, affordable car with clear upside. Priced to move for a buyer who wants a workable platform rather than overpaying for polish.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car fast. Sold as-is. Strong value at this price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with unmistakable character, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn presence that turns an ordinary driveway into the start of your next story. It\u2019s the kind of machine that invites a hands-on owner, a creative eye, or anyone who appreciates a vehicle with personality over polish. Great as a budget commuter, weekend project, or practical backup ride, it offers an affordable way to get into something with real presence and possibility. If you like your cars with grit, soul, and room to make it your own, this one is easy to root for.",
      "price": 6495.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable, no-nonsense transportation with solid value for the price. This vehicle shows its age and is being offered in as-is condition, making it a smart choice for a handy owner, first-time buyer, or anyone seeking an inexpensive way to get on the road. If you want a low-cost option with plenty of potential, this is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
